Talk To New Yogis - Problems From Fake Gurus. New Delhi, 19 February 1977.

Translation from Hindi:

Many of you have got realization, means you have started feeling vibrations in your hands.  I have already told you about the Chakras.  I know that many of you are feeling the vibrations in your hands, but many have still not felt it.  One thing I am not able to understand (disturbance ... Mr. Verma is telling you not to keep getting up from our seats.  It causes disturbance).

Those who have got realization, those who are feeling vibrations in their hands, and who have become thoughtless, if we tell them anything, then even those who have not got their realization should also listen, so that very soon they will also get realization.  As many as possible should get their realization.  And they will.  Mostly everyone gets it.

But if there are some people who have already collected some knowledge from other sources, regarding realization, regarding dharmas, and other ideas; for them it takes a longer time, because we have to bring them into the right path.  Like for someone who has proceeded on the wrong road, like the information that someone told Me just now, that was completely wrong, and these false gurus have been doing this business of misleading people into the wrong path.  All these people who go into these paths get completely destroyed.  Now those who have gone to their destruction ..  I am making an estimate that in this country alone, at least 3 crore people have been systematically sent to their destruction, and it is impossible to retrieve them.  And even if a few of them come to us, they come in the last stages of destruction, and we cannot do anything for them.  Then we just have to let them go and take their rebirth, and then get realization.

Now the experience that you have had there, will not be the same for others.  Some will get distressed and suffer, some will get influenced and do all what they are told to do by these various teachers.  We must understand that our attitude towards Sahaja Yoga should be that we have to achieve something out of it.  I have to take something inside, and that is why I have to receive something.  We have to recognize and accept the truth.  Or like someone said just now, “Shree Mataji You do not take any money” and this appeals to you and you come. But this feeling is not correct that we are gaining something out of you.   From your talk it appears that you feel we are obligated, not you.  Mostly people who say this is wrong with me, or that is wrong with me, and please correct it, we can understand. So the attitude should be that you have to acquire or achieve something from Sahaja Yoga

On one side you are there, and on the other are the deities.  The deities have their places already made on the Chakras.  If you have insulted or injured them by your behavior, then to awaken them again will require a lot of work and effort.  And whatever efforts we make to reinstate them and bring their attention on those chakras, if there is no acceptance or alignment from your side, then there is nothing we can do.

Suppose there is a man living in a house, just for a worldly example.  Because worldly people like worldly examples.  If you have to go to a minister to get a house, you have to go to him and ask him to give you a house.  But if the minister sees that you are not agreeable to take the house, then how will the minister sanction you a house.  In the same way we have to understand that in Sahaja Yoga God Almighty has made arrangements inside you to enlighten your lamp, and you are being invited to come inside and light your lamp.  But if you start arguing and hesitating about irrelevant things, that it is like this, and it is like that.  Like many people ask Me why I wear only white sarees.  If I wear red, then they will ask why red!  This is on the matter of human brains.  Because in Sahaja Yoga you have full freedom .  If you want to come inside you come, and if you want to leave, then you can go outside.  We are never going to stop you.  We will never catch your hand and make you stay.  If you come of your own free will and stay with us, we will look after you.  But if we force you nothing thing can happen, nor do we put any constraint on you to come.

Neither do we say that if you leave us and go, bad things will happen.  You come and improve yourself.  When you reach the understanding that there is no bandhan of Mother on us; I have come here, I am sitting here to take something from Mother.  The second thing is that now I have come to Mother, I must have faith in Her or not.  If you say that I do not have belief or faith in You, but you give me, then why should I give.  My relationship with the gods is that of a Mother.  If a Mother says the word “son”, then nothing more is required.  But all these great ones who are sitting around all of you, can know at once, all those who have shraddha (faith) towards Mother.  You will have to have a little faith.  I am telling you the inside story.  You will have to have a little bit of faith in Me.  Otherwise it wont work out.  Secondly, if there is anything wrong with your health, some illness or something else, it will take longer.  If you have any other problems like some may have mental problems, some who are possessed, in whom there may be bhoots or badhas.  Others have other problems which may be a hindrance.  But the most difficult are those, like the gentleman who showed Me the letter. These poor souls get ensnared by going to the wrong gurus and bowing their heads to them.  The Kundalinis of such people do not rise at all.

[Shri Mataji asks for a letter to be read. A yogi reads the following:]

English part: 

Dear Mataji,

A few years ago, Swami Muktananda initiated me in his yoga. He calls it Siddha Yoga. It is supposed to be a form of Kundalini Yoga. Since then, I have been suffering from a heavy pressure in the head and spine, inability to think clearly or concentrate, some sort of movement in the backbone which certainly isn't pleasant, nervousness, difficulty in facing people and situations, bad memory, obsession with the past and some sort of involuntary fixation with sex. Perhaps the Kundalini has been activated. Whatever it is, there is nothing spiritual about it. There is no sign of peace or silence or impersonal love. I am sure I have not benefitted spiritually through my contact with him. For all I know I was a better person spiritually before I met him. Would You please help me at least to get normal.

Pranamas.

Ibrahim Khan - A seeker.

Shri Mataji: Absolutely correct. And I must congratulate him for this bold action that he has taken; is a very bold action. Of course we have some others here who will share his thoughts, very much who have suffered. And those-

Yogi: He's here.

Shri Mataji: He's here. And there are many who have suffered on account, they have taken him out and they are much better now. And they are very good and absolutely what you have said is correct. It has to be a spiritual experience of bliss and joy, first thing. It has to be, secondly, a thing that enriches you, makes you much wiser, makes you sharper and alert. It has to be a energy-giving thing. Apart from that you are made a much better person; there's a regular transformation in your being. Now there are, you will be surprised like this, at least sixteen big ones, sixteen of them, they are doing this kind of job. And people are sending thousands of rupees to these people, thousands! He came from Lond- some place, America or somewhere, he has brought crores of foreign exchange. Crores of foreign exchange, how did he manage? You have been a religious man and that's why you have been opposing it. And by God's grace you are going to get the reality, no doubt.

The person who is initiated and is not a religious man will get into the mood. He'll start misbehaving, he'll take to ganja [marijuana â€” ed], he'll take to all kinds of drugs, he will take to bad sexual habits, he'll be perverted man, he will start becoming a smuggler and a thief and he'll do all the things. But a man who is a really, a religious man by heart will resist it and because of resistance he will get all these symptoms. But I'm happy you have resisted him and I promise that I will give you realization here and here. And I'm very happy that you have done it. But so many like this. I've already told you that even with gross calculation three crores [30 million - ED] already on a way to doom. Of course some are going to be saved not out of those three crores are absolutely towards their doom. Then they come and argue with Me. The thing is, they have done so much wrong to themselves by wrong things and then they come and argue with me; this is something I can't understand. You cannot argue it out. If I can cure you I will give My life, every... every part of My being, I would say, every drop of My blood to save humankind. I will go out of the way for saving them, but you must understand that this is not spirituality. Spirituality is promised in all the scriptures whether it is Koran, it is Geeta, anywhere, that you are born again. You become a transformed personality and a higher personality.

