Now all of you sit with your hands like this. This is for people who have got their realization.  You don’t have to do anything special.  In Sahaja Yoga you know all the arrangements are built in within you.  Only it is a matter of igniting.  All the system is built in within you, seven chakras and if there is a problem in a chakra, then the Kundalini does not rise.  Otherwise it is sitting in 3.1/2 coils, and rises on Her own, and does the complete job.  If there is a problem in any chakra, She stops there and repairs any damage.  Sometimes She can even be seen pulsating at a particular chakra.  Tomorrow I will show you.  Wherever there is a catch in a chakra, Kundalini can be seen at that spot, doing Her job.  I am telling you about the state after realization.  Those who have just got their realization should listen carefully and also those who have not yet got it, should also listen.  But all of you should keep your hands open like this.  All.  I had told you in the beginning that the Kundalini is inside you like this cord.  Now you are like a computer, and your cord has to be connected to the mains.  I have connected it through the Brahmarandhra, in the middle.  Now what information is coming to you through this new connection, like Jung has said, there is the Universal Unconscious, and from the Unconscious messages keep coming.  Then he says there is a Shakti called Universal Unconsciousness, which we call as the All Pervading Love of the Paramatma, or God Almighty.  (someone asks “Universal Unconsciousness?”).  Unconscious!  It is called Universal Unconscious, because it is not in our consciousness.  So it is called Unconscious (A-chetan), which has not yet come into our chetana (consciousness).  Once it comes into our chetana, then Universal Consciousness comes into us.  This does not come by any lectures.  It happens.  There is a happening that takes place inside you.  This begins to flow inside you.  And you come into a new, absolutely new, awareness.  Like a blind man cannot see.  Also a human being knows what is beauty.  Animals do not.  So in this way you come into a new awareness state, where you become Collectively Conscious.  Means, what happens, that on your hands you can feel the chakras of others and the state of their Kundalini.  Instantaneously.  At that moment.  Like as soon as you get your realization, you can put your hands towards a0nother person and read the state of his chakras.

Now this knowledge is subjective.  There are two kinds of knowledge.  One, which you understand from outside, and the other which you know from the inside.  Like, if we are the manager of an office, then we know everything abot that office.  But if someone comes from outside, he can only see what is outside.  But the man who works in the office, knows it from inside.  This is how it works.  When you put your hands towards any realized soul, you will get cool breeze on your hands.  On the fingers you have five chakras.  This is the sixth, and this is the seventh.  This is the first chakra, the Mooladhara, which is the chakra there on the chart.  Mooladhara Chakra is the seat of Shri Ganesha.  Now there is a left and a right.  The two hands have a left side and a right side.  There is the Left Sympathetic Nervous System and the Right Sympathetic Nervous System.  Now, there was a need for someone to teach you the decoding of the system.  So I have come.  Because if no one teaches you how to decode the system, how will you work your computer.

Now in the hand, in this place, is the Mooladhara Chakra.  Mooladhara Chakra is placed right down.  As I told you, it has four petals.  This is the seat of Shri Ganesha.  Now, all of you realized souls, ask a question – Is Mooladhara Chakra the seat of Shri Ganesha.  Ask Shri Ganesha, “Is Mool-adhara Your place?  Are You on this Chakra?”  You will get a response.  As realized souls, if you ask, you will get strong vibrations.  Because the question is a solemn one.  Are you feeling it.  Do you get extra vibrations your hands?  More than before?  Ask Kundalini.  Just ask the question.  Put your hands towards Me and ask.  Is it coming.  In this place?  Is something happening here.  For those who have just got their realisatio, it should happen.  When you place your hands on others you will feel it.  Sometimes when you put your hands towards a person, even a child, you will have a burning sensation on your fingers.  This left side is the emotional side, and the right side is the physical side.  If you feel a burning on the emotional side, the left side, it means that someone has used bad techniques to raise his kundalini.  Mostly those who try wrong methods of raising the Kundalini, they have a burning on this left hand.  Because they use sublimation of sex on the left side, and completely ruin this chakra.  So the catch, the burning, is here.  And if you get it on the other hand, the right hand, there is some problem with that person about sex.  If it gets numb, then there may be impotency.  If there is numbness, then we can understand that that man is impotent.  And if it comes higher up on the right side, then the person is suffering from constipation.  As you practice more and more, your hands will become very sensitive.  And those who are born realized, even if you blindfold them, they will register the catches.

I am just telling you in a general way.  I cannot tell you in detail just now.  I am writing a book in which I will explain everything in detail, and you will be able to understand it all.  Now these two fingers, thumbs, they represent the Swadishtana Chakra.  This one is the Swadishtana.  The thumbs of the right hand, the right side of this chakra, is creativity as I told you.  The Swadishtana is the seat of Shri Brahmadeva and his Shakti is Shree Saraswati.  If a man thinks too much, or plans a lot, he uses the energy of this chakra.  And the chakra which is shown in the thub, rotates around, and on the edges whatever organs are there it supplies energy.  Means the kidneys, upper and lower part of the liver, and your spleen.  And the uterus in women.  It looks after all these organs.  Now if this chakra gets a catch, then you can know that you have diabetes, in a general way, or some problem with the spleen.  When both sides of this chakra are caught up badly, then cancer has set in; and with the overactivity of this chakra it becomes galloping.  When this happens we can understand that some outside badha or entity, has entered and is working on this chakra.  (Someone interrupts).  So, you understand.

Now if there is a lady, and her husband’s first wife has died, just suppose, and she did not have any children, and her husband marries another woman, the first lady dies in an accident or unnatural circumstances, and she never had a child, so her entity might enter into this second wife, and she may come back.  The mental side.  Now mentally if she is disturbed about it, and thinks about it, that she had no child, I also may not have a child – if she has a fear about it, it will act on the uterus and she will also not have children.  This is the emotional side of it.

English part: 

If there is a lady and her, you see her, the first wife has died. Supposing take a question, and she has had no children or something like she died as an atrupta atma and the husband marries another woman. And the first lady died in a mess or in a atrupta way and she never had a child. So she, her entity might enter into this woman's entity and she may come into that woman. You see this is a, this is a emotional side, so emotionally if she is disturbed about it, if she thinks about it that she had no child, "I may not have a child," if she has a fear like that or something, it will act on the uterus and she will also not have children. That's the emotional side of it. And the right hand side if you have a uterus trouble and uterus problem or anything like that, then also you cannot have. But when these two meet together, a galloping sort of a movement starts of both the sympathetic nervous system and then you can say that it is a cancer has been set in. But cancer is set into us every moment and is destroyed every moment by parasympathetic. Because if the activity of the sympathetic nervous system is the cause of cancer means everybody has it. You see, is possible it is and the more - if you do it over-activity, more than what is needed - it sets in.

A man who is a great planner say, he's a very great planner and he's a very great this thing, and he gets, sort of all his time devoted to work and work and work, he develops a deficiency in the spleen because this also supplies to the spleen. And that's how spleen and then your liver and kidney all put together give you the disease known as diabetes. Diabetes is only caused among people who think too much. Diabetes will not happen among the people who are poor because they don't sit down and think and bother about things. So diabetes is caused among such people. Mostly it is caused among men, less among women. Doctors do not know the cause of diabetes. Now if I tell them Swadhisthana Chakra and Brahmadeva's activities, they will say, "Mataji, this is beyond us."

But if tell them imbalance, if there is imbalance in life, if there is imbalance in life, then it is caused. It is due to the imbalance in life because such a man, you see when he starts planning too much, thinking too much, he has no time for emotional activities. Like, you see he has no time for his children, he has no time for his wife, he has no time for anybody to, you see express themself. If he can have the balance between the two, if he's a very loving man then the balance is maintained. But mostly what happens, a man who takes to hard work, he has no time for his children. Then if he gets a little time for his children, children think, "Oh it's a great thing." And such a, such a personality has diabetes. And the diabetes has such a vicious circle that it goes on increasing and increasing and increasing. Then it increases up to the - you see it can go up to the eyes you may start getting very weak eyes with diabetes. And I mean anything can happen because you start, lets say the sugar in the... sugar in the blood is not consumed, so for such a person who suffers from diabetes there's a very simple method, if he's a realized soul. You see, if he's a realized soul - that's one "if" is there. If he's not, then nothing can work out; all these things are for realized people.

You have to put your - now as you say that your right side is weak, your right is being used too much, your left side is weak. So what you have to do is to put the left hand towards the photograph raise your left hand and put it to the right hand, like this. Now what happens when the left side is weak, you see there is... on the top of the head there are two balloon-like structures, one of them goes on to the front and another goes at the back. But one comes from the right, another comes from the left. Now the one which comes on the left because it crosses over, so the left one is responsible for the right hand, and the right one is responsible for the left hand. So by doing like this what you do is to press your ego backward and that's how you get a complete balance there and the Kundalini rises in between. Because one side is too much pressed and the another side is suppressed. Raise your left hand side like this, all right, raising it like this. Left hand side, left hand, left hand yes teek hai. Left with the right hand you will have to raise.

